      <section otherprops="IEC" class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Overview Screen in Manual Bypass
Operation</title>
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <table outputclass="font:10" class="- topic/table ">
               <tgroup cols="1" class="- topic/tgroup ">
                  <colspec colname="col1" colwidth="100.00*" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                  <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <screen xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre ui-d/screen ">Manual Bypass Normal  OperationLoad 058%  Cap. 093%405Uin  xxxUout  xxHz</screen>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                  </tbody>
               </tgroup>
            </table>
            <p class="- topic/p ">The second line indicates the state of the isolated system: <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Standby</uicontrol>, <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Normal Operation</uicontrol>, <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Battery Operation</uicontrol>, <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Static Bypass Operation</uicontrol>. Input voltage, output voltage, and output frequency are not shown
in manual bypass operation.</p>
         </sectiondiv>
      </section>
      <section otherprops="UL" class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Overview Screen in Maintenance Bypass
Operation </title>
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">
               <table outputclass="font:10" class="- topic/table ">
